.row
  .col-xs-12
    .panel.panel-warning
      .panel-heading
        %h4 {{ cards.sources[optionId] }}
      .panel-body
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            .row.text-center
              Dies ist die Ansicht der Quelle {{cards.sources[optionId] }}. Hier beschreiben wir kurz,
              was man dort findet und was man ggf. bei der Suche in der Quelle beachten muss.
              %br
              %br
              %button.btn.btn-success Ab zu {{cards.sources[optionId]}}
.row
  .col-xs-12
    .panel.panel-warning
      .panel-heading
        %h4 Quellen
      .panel-body
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            %form.form-horizontal{:role => "form"}
              .form-group
                .col-xs-3
                  %select
                    %option Alle
                    %option Freie Quellen
                    %option Datenbanken
                    %option Literatur
                    %option Experten
                    %option Die Massen
                .col-xs-3
                  %input{ :type=>"checkbox" } VorschlÃ¤ge anderer User?
                .col-xs-4
                  %input.form-control{"ng-model" => "noteknowledge"}/
                .col-xs-2
                  %button.btn.btn-warning Filter
        %hr
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            .row.text-center
            %div{"ng-model" => "cards.sources", "ui-sortable" => "sortableOptions"}
              .col-xs-4{"ng-repeat" => "card in cards.sources"}
                .panel.panel-warning.is-draggable
                  .panel-heading
                    %a{:href => "#/source/{{$index}}", 'ng-class' => "{active: $location.path() == '/source'}"} {{ card }}
                  .panel-body
                    Einige Worte zu {{ card }}
